com.erudika.para.persistence

Class IndexBasedDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.erudika.para.persistence.IndexBasedDAO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DAO

    @Singleton
public class IndexBasedDAO
extends Object
implements DAO
    An implementation of the DAO interface used for local development only. It uses is based on the Search implementation. Objects are stored in the index rather than in a data store. Note: This implementation doesn't work well with apps sharing one index (app.isSharingIndex() must be false).
    Author:
    Alex Bogdanovski [alex@erudika.com]
